Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\an7\move(180,185,178,186,0,300)\fs13\frz13\1c707070\bord0}今天我在世博会的会场组装好Gun制造2号机了\N终于走到这一步了\N请姐姐一定要来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她现在来东京了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你为什么还要对她不管不顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有对她不管不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说出了事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子太过平凡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是无法继承我的意志制造机器人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(355,109,343,109)\fs14\frz6\bord0}干线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(406,236,394,236)\fs10\frz6\1cB7B7B7\bord0}距离目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(488,226,476,226)\fs10\frz6\1cB7B7B7\bord0}预测抵达时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她越是努力  就越会感到自己的无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不是说让你好好照顾这样的亚希吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  真是人山人海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  2020年东京世博会「～梦・创・造・博～」正式开幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本届世博会最大的看点就是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本届世博会别名机器人世博
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会场内聚集了来自世界各地的巨型机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引了许多观众前来参观
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有冲击力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这个比较起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,90)\fs22\frz-8\1c000000\bord0}宇宙糖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,123)\fs22\frz-8\1c000000\bord0}种子岛Robo部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就只需要使用靠爸爸的关系托人制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个特制小型激光供电枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an8\fs18\1c000000\3cFFFFFF}Gunvarrel制作日记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\1c000000\3cFFFFFF}Gunvarrel制作日记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子太过平凡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天见过爱理之后又有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来的好像挺晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  只是还有点疲劳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这个Gunvarrel是个什么玩意儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel不就是那个杀人犯监督做出来的动画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(545,110)\fs16\1c903318\3cFFFFFF\b1}种子岛Robo部\N×\N宇宙糖有限公司\N{\1c2C1AC3}展出Gunvarrel试作2号机！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么把这种东西弄到展会上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑乃宫妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小充…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没撞到头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  快给我滚出展会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太不自觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这杀人机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好痛  好痛  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得…  有点伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel居然被讨厌到这种地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明机器人是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)\fs16}Wyvern
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-90分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是艾克索斯克尔顿公司展出的概念模型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SUMERAGI通过指控系统——也就是手指来控制6条腿的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打家看这边～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,种子岛Robo部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来将启动我们的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我先来介绍一下这台机器人的制造经过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在距今大约9年前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「实体大型Gunvarrel制造计划」启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我也知道在现在以Gunvarrel作为原型并不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(520,210,467,210)\fs12\frz-29\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord1}「实体大型Gunvarrel制造计划」\N记录相册
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(370,305,317,305)\fs12\frz-36\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord1}请随意阅览
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希  你不觉得话说得有点多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众都快跑光了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.1}但描述一下我们那充满了爱与勇气和荣誉的努力过程会比较有冲击力…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  Gun制造2号机  启动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,横行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  好丑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那边那位说「好丑啊」的小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就抱着被骗的心态用IRUO.看一下Gun制造2号机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有真正的Gunvarrel！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gun制造2号机  一击破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元气一发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾风怒涛  元气一发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是Gunvarrel就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆史  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  我想再多看一会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈要是知道我给你看了Gunvarrel的话可是会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐  再来一次  再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再表演一次元气一发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你啦  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾风怒涛  元气一发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打…  打家好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…  请朵朵直角！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是阿昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问您现在感想如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我们还要更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我会以头奖为目标的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  这可真是大胆的宣言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.1}濑乃宫亚希穗同学的姐姐是出演艾克索斯克尔顿公司广告的美纱希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有告知她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就宣言一下吧  我想她应该已经来到会场内了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  不  你说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  以上便是对种子岛Robo部  濑乃宫亚希穗同学的采访
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾克索斯克尔顿公司的休息室是在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你最好还是过一阵子再去见美纱姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,84)\frz-12\fs20\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord2}内部人员通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是我啊  亚希穗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们是姐妹  这么说可能很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们已经七年没见面了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候我还只是个小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你是没认出来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你看到我制造的机器人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gun制造2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是Robo部的大家一起制造出来的机器人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸好久都没有参与火箭发射的工作了  干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过身来看看这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这些话的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑乃宫美纱希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样举起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭还没升空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到没有  濑乃宫  给我举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
